text: John Kitching is a male former athlete who competed for England. ==Athletics career== He represented England in the high jump at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games in Cardiff, Wales. ==Personal life== He was a member of the Achilles Club and also threw the javelin. ==References== Category:English male high jumpers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games
title: John Kitching (athlete)
